  ],
  "subject": [],
  "abstracts": [
    {
      "note": "summary",
      "abstract": "Provides that motor vehicle rental companies be entitled to establish non-liability for toll violations, administrative fees, and fines by providing a rental or lease agreement as prima facie evidence that a lessee was the vehicle operator."
    }
